25|$|Phil Jackson reached 1,000 career wins on December 25, 2008 {{against the}} Boston Celtics. With 1,423 games coached, {{he became the}} fastest coach in NBA history to reach 1,000 wins, surpassing former Lakers coach <b>Pat</b> <b>Riley.</b>|$|E
